1
00:01:53,680 --> 00:01:54,900
Play these ones in a row

2
00:01:54,900 --> 00:01:56,040
And nobody can stop you

3
00:01:56,040 --> 00:01:56,659
Right

4
00:01:56,920 --> 00:01:57,519
Shunzi

5
00:01:57,799 --> 00:01:58,480
Yusheng

6
00:01:59,319 --> 00:02:00,219
That's not fair

7
00:02:00,620 --> 00:02:02,480
You just saw my cards

8
00:02:02,680 --> 00:02:03,980
Then went to help him

9
00:02:04,560 --> 00:02:05,400
This is cards

10
00:02:05,400 --> 00:02:06,159
Not chess

11
00:02:06,159 --> 00:02:07,340
It's all exposed now

12
00:02:07,340 --> 00:02:08,159
Sorry

13
00:02:08,500 --> 00:02:09,340
Professor Fan, too

14
00:02:09,340 --> 00:02:10,379
Sorry about that, Boss Li

15
00:02:10,400 --> 00:02:11,460
I'll help you check your cards

16
00:02:11,460 --> 00:02:12,500
We won't let him look

17
00:02:12,500 --> 00:02:12,939
Okay

18
00:02:13,520 --> 00:02:14,259
Help me take a look

19
00:02:14,819 --> 00:02:15,680
How should I play this?

20
00:02:15,979 --> 00:02:16,439
This one

21
00:02:18,460 --> 00:02:18,979
Okay

22
00:02:20,379 --> 00:02:21,680
Hello? Mommy

23
00:02:25,879 --> 00:02:27,199
Any new progress?

24
00:02:32,740 --> 00:02:33,539
No

25
00:02:33,639 --> 00:02:35,699
I haven't thought it through yet

26
00:02:35,780 --> 00:02:36,340
You and Dad

27
00:02:36,340 --> 00:02:37,919
Can't decide for me again

28
00:02:40,680 --> 00:02:41,379
Alright

29
00:02:41,719 --> 00:02:43,379
Can we talk about this later?

30
00:02:44,680 --> 00:02:46,219
I'm busy right now

31
00:02:47,259 --> 00:02:47,680
Okay

32
00:02:47,819 --> 00:02:48,580
Bye-bye, Mommy

33
00:02:57,159 --> 00:02:57,860
Yingzi

34
00:02:58,680 --> 00:02:59,759
That phone call of yours

35
00:03:00,219 --> 00:03:01,460
Look at this great hand

36
00:03:01,460 --> 00:03:02,520
It's completely ruined

37
00:03:02,580 --> 00:03:03,439
Sorry, Boss Li

38
00:03:03,439 --> 00:03:04,159
Coming

39
00:03:07,580 --> 00:03:08,379
Is it about

40
00:03:08,879 --> 00:03:10,960
your family discussing you going abroad for grad school?

41
00:03:11,500 --> 00:03:12,699
It's hardly a discussion.

42
00:03:12,979 --> 00:03:13,919
It's an order.

43
00:03:14,300 --> 00:03:15,039
So you...

44
00:03:15,719 --> 00:03:16,840
have to leave right after graduation?

45
00:03:18,819 --> 00:03:20,159
That's what my dad wants.

46
00:03:20,639 --> 00:03:22,120
But what do *you* want?

47
00:03:22,479 --> 00:03:22,919
Me?

48
00:03:24,280 --> 00:03:25,719
I don't really have a plan.

49
00:03:27,280 --> 00:03:28,439
Actually,

50
00:03:29,080 --> 00:03:31,699
our domestic education standards aren't low.

51
00:03:32,180 --> 00:03:33,759
We have so many professors

52
00:03:33,979 --> 00:03:34,560
and doctoral supervisors.

53
00:03:35,379 --> 00:03:37,680
You don't have to go abroad to further your studies.

54
00:03:37,919 --> 00:03:39,120
Don't you agree, Professor Fan?

55
00:03:40,800 --> 00:03:41,919
I actually think

56
00:03:41,979 --> 00:03:43,620
going out to broaden your horizons

57
00:03:43,800 --> 00:03:44,680
is a good thing.

58
00:03:44,939 --> 00:03:45,139
I mean,

59
00:03:45,139 --> 00:03:46,479
read ten thousand books, travel ten thousand miles.

60
00:03:46,479 --> 00:03:46,879
Right?

61
00:03:47,819 --> 00:03:48,719
I think

62
00:03:48,939 --> 00:03:50,139
going abroad is useless.

63
00:03:51,680 --> 00:03:53,979
Grandpa Boss Li's opinion is important too.

64
00:03:54,159 --> 00:03:54,759
Come on,

65
00:03:55,020 --> 00:03:56,319
tell us all about it.

66
00:03:56,620 --> 00:03:57,840
Especially for Yingzi.

67
00:03:59,900 --> 00:04:01,340
Since you've achieved academic success,

68
00:04:02,039 --> 00:04:03,780
you should, as soon as possible,

69
00:04:03,840 --> 00:04:04,680
devote yourself to

70
00:04:04,719 --> 00:04:07,000
the current modernization efforts.

71
00:04:07,860 --> 00:04:09,259
Use the knowledge you've learned

72
00:04:10,439 --> 00:04:11,419
for the country,

73
00:04:11,599 --> 00:04:12,500
for society,

74
00:04:12,620 --> 00:04:13,560
and for the people,

75
00:04:13,740 --> 00:04:15,039
to make more contributions.

76
00:04:16,160 --> 00:04:18,779
I think going abroad to learn more skills

77
00:04:18,860 --> 00:04:20,980
and then returning to serve the country isn't too late.

78
00:04:22,300 --> 00:04:24,540
I don't think Yingzi should go.

79
00:04:24,680 --> 00:04:26,139
It's so chaotic out there.

80
00:04:26,220 --> 00:04:27,839
What don't we have here?

81
00:04:27,959 --> 00:04:29,139
Why do you have to go out

82
00:04:29,139 --> 00:04:30,980
and get caught in a school shooting?

83
00:04:31,720 --> 00:04:33,240
I agree with Xiao Cai's analysis.

84
00:04:34,040 --> 00:04:36,259
Going abroad is no small matter.

85
00:04:36,879 --> 00:04:39,180
It could change your entire life.

86
00:04:40,160 --> 00:04:41,379
You know me,

87
00:04:41,399 --> 00:04:42,959
I've never been very decisive.

88
00:04:43,259 --> 00:04:44,680
After listening to all your advice,

89
00:04:45,860 --> 00:04:47,420
I'm even less sure of what to do.

90
00:04:48,939 --> 00:04:49,660
Yingzi,

91
00:04:49,939 --> 00:04:51,500
this is a major life decision.

92
00:04:52,220 --> 00:04:53,759
You must make the decision yourself

93
00:04:53,959 --> 00:04:55,279
so you won't regret it later.

94
00:04:56,120 --> 00:04:57,699
When I was your age,

95
00:04:57,920 --> 00:05:00,019
just because I took one wrong step,

96
00:05:00,459 --> 00:05:01,279
I've regretted it my whole life.

97
00:05:01,399 --> 00:05:02,540
Really?

98
00:05:03,420 --> 00:05:04,019
Absolutely.

99
00:05:04,259 --> 00:05:04,939
Otherwise,

100
00:05:05,019 --> 00:05:06,579
why would I end up like this?

101
00:05:06,779 --> 00:05:07,459
Hanging out with you...

102
00:05:07,699 --> 00:05:08,100
No,

103
00:05:08,360 --> 00:05:09,459
hanging out with Old Li.

104
00:05:11,279 --> 00:05:12,240
What's wrong with playing cards with me?

105
00:05:12,720 --> 00:05:14,259
That's your good fortune.

106
00:05:15,939 --> 00:05:17,439
It's just one wrong step.

107
00:05:17,920 --> 00:05:19,800
Like no one else has ever made a mistake.

108
00:05:20,920 --> 00:05:22,459
You even argue about this?

109
00:05:22,720 --> 00:05:23,939
I'm not arguing.

110
00:05:24,100 --> 00:05:25,819
I really did make a mistake.

111
00:05:26,740 --> 00:05:27,639
But so what?

112
00:05:28,079 --> 00:05:29,439
I've regretted it for half my life.

113
00:05:31,860 --> 00:05:33,079
We've all been there.

114
00:05:33,519 --> 00:05:34,579
You too?

115
00:05:34,680 --> 00:05:35,579
Of course.

116
00:05:36,660 --> 00:05:37,879
Back then, Director Zhang...

117
00:05:38,100 --> 00:05:40,279
the one who won the Golden Cat Award...

118
00:05:40,279 --> 00:05:41,199
for that movie.

119
00:05:41,360 --> 00:05:43,040
He came to me first.

120
00:05:44,160 --> 00:05:45,379
He wanted me to play Cixi.

121
00:05:46,839 --> 00:05:48,860
Playing Cixi at such a young age.

122
00:05:49,139 --> 00:05:50,319
The young Cixi.

123
00:05:51,319 --> 00:05:52,519
Director Zhang had his eye on me.

124
00:05:53,079 --> 00:05:55,860
If I had done that movie back then,

125
00:05:56,180 --> 00:05:58,620
I'd be a multi-award-winning actress now.

126
00:06:01,300 --> 00:06:02,920
But Director Zhang...

127
00:06:03,000 --> 00:06:04,259
The casting couch? You refused?

128
00:06:04,360 --> 00:06:04,860
Good for you.

129
00:06:06,240 --> 00:06:07,819
What are you thinking?

130
00:06:08,279 --> 00:06:09,860
It's just that Director Zhang and I

131
00:06:10,980 --> 00:06:12,800
didn't get along at all.

132
00:06:13,199 --> 00:06:13,800
Let's not talk about it.

133
00:06:13,959 --> 00:06:14,519
Let's play cards.

134
00:06:15,959 --> 00:06:17,500
Speaking of wrong steps,

135
00:06:18,019 --> 00:06:18,579
actually,

136
00:06:18,819 --> 00:06:19,920
I made a mistake too.

137
00:06:20,680 --> 00:06:23,980
Back then, a really handsome guy liked me.

138
00:06:26,740 --> 00:06:28,620
I let that opportunity slip away.

139
00:06:29,500 --> 00:06:30,459
Now,

140
00:06:30,660 --> 00:06:32,660
he's already a Chief Engineer.

141
00:06:33,279 --> 00:06:35,600
If I hadn't missed that chance back then,

142
00:06:35,600 --> 00:06:36,540
and married him,

143
00:06:37,060 --> 00:06:39,480
I wouldn't have ended up marrying into the Chen family,

144
00:06:39,480 --> 00:06:40,939
and being a widow all my life.

145
00:06:42,060 --> 00:06:42,920
Oh, life...

146
00:06:43,620 --> 00:06:43,899
Sei-

147
00:06:44,000 --> 00:06:45,560
Seizing opportunities is too important.

148
00:06:46,839 --> 00:06:47,699
Old Li, it's your turn.

149
00:06:50,259 --> 00:06:50,500
It's your turn.

150
00:06:50,500 --> 00:06:51,220
Play a card.

151
00:07:05,139 --> 00:07:05,779
Stop looking.

152
00:07:06,360 --> 00:07:07,699
Rush over there and confess.

153
00:07:07,920 --> 00:07:08,360
You...

154
00:07:09,079 --> 00:07:10,500
You are my... right?

155
00:07:10,779 --> 00:07:11,759
Grandpa?

156
00:07:11,779 --> 00:07:12,620
Nonsense.

157
00:07:12,740 --> 00:07:13,660
Am I that old?

158
00:07:15,420 --> 00:07:16,540
Actually, pretty close.

159
00:07:17,420 --> 00:07:18,720
I am you.

160
00:07:19,560 --> 00:07:21,120
You, forty years from now.

161
00:07:21,939 --> 00:07:22,620
I know.

162
00:07:22,819 --> 00:07:23,860
You came today...

163
00:07:23,920 --> 00:07:25,199
to confess your love to Jing Xian.

164
00:07:25,519 --> 00:07:26,379
I came specifically to help you.

165
00:07:26,699 --> 00:07:27,399
Alright then.

166
00:07:28,160 --> 00:07:30,079
Help me chase that Guo Lixin away right now.

167
00:07:30,259 --> 00:07:31,120
Guo Lixin?

168
00:07:31,180 --> 00:07:33,319
He's on the school team for Throwing Events.

169
00:07:34,199 --> 00:07:35,439
Even you couldn't beat him.

170
00:07:35,680 --> 00:07:38,100
I'm an old man over sixty; fight him?

171
00:07:39,360 --> 00:07:40,379
Then how can you help me?

172
00:07:41,060 --> 00:07:43,040
I... am here to remind you.

173
00:07:43,379 --> 00:07:44,319
This is the critical moment...

174
00:07:44,439 --> 00:07:45,980
that decides your whole life.

175
00:07:46,060 --> 00:07:47,060
You must seize it.

176
00:07:47,519 --> 00:07:48,540
Confess loudly!

177
00:07:49,360 --> 00:07:50,660
Actually, Jing Xian...

178
00:07:50,860 --> 00:07:52,180
likes you.

179
00:07:52,500 --> 00:07:53,139
Me?

180
00:07:53,480 --> 00:07:54,180
Us.

181
00:07:54,680 --> 00:07:55,360
Really?

182
00:07:56,079 --> 00:07:56,860
She likes...

183
00:07:57,500 --> 00:07:58,019
you.

184
00:07:58,579 --> 00:07:59,240
Us.

185
00:08:01,819 --> 00:08:03,560
But if I just go up and confess like this,

186
00:08:04,500 --> 00:08:06,220
what if she rejects me?

187
00:08:06,819 --> 00:08:08,639
What if Guo Lixin beats me up?

188
00:08:08,639 --> 00:08:09,339
Don't be afraid.

189
00:08:09,740 --> 00:08:11,500
Guo Lixin didn't beat me up later on.

190
00:08:12,680 --> 00:08:14,240
He has his weakness.

191
00:08:15,680 --> 00:08:16,199
Okay.

192
00:08:17,579 --> 00:08:18,540
Then I'll...

193
00:08:21,160 --> 00:08:22,600
I'm still a bit...

194
00:08:22,699 --> 00:08:23,279
What's wrong?

195
00:08:24,699 --> 00:08:26,439
Since you are me,

196
00:08:26,779 --> 00:08:28,100
you should know clearly.

197
00:08:28,500 --> 00:08:30,279
That's just our personality.

198
00:08:30,779 --> 00:08:31,899
Of course I know.

199
00:08:31,899 --> 00:08:32,600
Cowardly.

200
00:08:32,659 --> 00:08:33,600
Socially anxious.

201
00:08:33,659 --> 00:08:34,360
A wimp.

202
00:08:34,620 --> 00:08:36,580
That's why I came to encourage you!

203
00:08:36,820 --> 00:08:38,000
Seize this opportunity.

204
00:08:38,139 --> 00:08:38,820
Otherwise,

205
00:08:39,179 --> 00:08:40,080
in the future, we...

206
00:08:40,360 --> 00:08:41,639
will have no children,

207
00:08:41,919 --> 00:08:43,019
be all alone,

208
00:08:43,179 --> 00:08:44,679
and die of old age in a nursing home,

209
00:08:44,940 --> 00:08:46,480
playing cards with a bunch of old people.

210
00:08:46,620 --> 00:08:47,340
Do you understand?

211
00:08:47,860 --> 00:08:49,580
Is this your way of encouraging me?

212
00:08:50,159 --> 00:08:52,039
This is practically intimidation!

213
00:08:52,759 --> 00:08:53,460
Besides,

214
00:08:54,080 --> 00:08:55,399
we're such a catch,

215
00:08:55,639 --> 00:08:57,639
how could we end up all alone?

216
00:08:57,919 --> 00:08:58,720
Cut the crap.

217
00:08:59,100 --> 00:08:59,580
Go!

218
00:09:01,179 --> 00:09:02,580
Watch where you're going!

219
00:09:04,659 --> 00:09:05,460
Dacheng?

220
00:09:07,940 --> 00:09:08,559
Xiao Fan?

221
00:09:09,299 --> 00:09:10,279
What are you doing here?

222
00:09:10,419 --> 00:09:11,179
I...

223
00:09:11,559 --> 00:09:12,159
Nothing.

224
00:09:17,919 --> 00:09:18,639
Brother Guo

225
00:09:19,320 --> 00:09:21,340
I just came to take a look

226
00:09:21,720 --> 00:09:23,980
Are you dating Jing Xian?

227
00:09:24,240 --> 00:09:24,840
That's right

228
00:09:24,960 --> 00:09:25,659
Why?

229
00:09:25,899 --> 00:09:27,299
Do I need your permission?

230
00:09:27,399 --> 00:09:28,100
Da Cheng

231
00:09:28,379 --> 00:09:29,480
Speak if you have something to say

232
00:09:30,980 --> 00:09:31,740
I...

233
00:09:32,399 --> 00:09:33,200
I...

234
00:09:35,360 --> 00:09:36,240
Old Fan

235
00:09:36,620 --> 00:09:37,940
What should I do?

236
00:09:38,000 --> 00:09:39,980
Why are you such a coward?

237
00:09:41,519 --> 00:09:42,340
We...

238
00:09:43,220 --> 00:09:44,539
Is it "we" who are cowardly?

239
00:09:44,600 --> 00:09:45,500
It's just you

240
00:09:45,500 --> 00:09:45,840
I...

241
00:09:46,220 --> 00:09:46,980
Back then

242
00:09:47,279 --> 00:09:50,080
If I had known Jing Xian liked me deep down

243
00:09:50,200 --> 00:09:51,899
I definitely would have taken that step

244
00:09:52,379 --> 00:09:52,840
I...

245
00:09:54,059 --> 00:09:54,519
He...

246
00:09:55,059 --> 00:09:55,460
I...

247
00:09:56,440 --> 00:09:58,259
I really can't take that step

248
00:09:58,639 --> 00:09:59,279
You...

249
00:09:59,620 --> 00:10:00,220
Come here

250
00:10:00,519 --> 00:10:01,100
I'll tell you

251
00:10:01,179 --> 00:10:02,879
some key information

252
00:10:11,679 --> 00:10:12,519
Really?

253
00:10:14,259 --> 00:10:14,740
Okay

254
00:10:15,460 --> 00:10:16,039
Don't worry

255
00:10:16,379 --> 00:10:18,580
I'm going to take this crucial step in life

256
00:10:25,139 --> 00:10:26,679
I like Jing Xian

257
00:10:26,899 --> 00:10:28,100
And she likes me too

258
00:10:28,679 --> 00:10:30,440
Please stay away from her from now on

259
00:10:30,720 --> 00:10:33,879
You'll have to get past me first

260
00:10:34,100 --> 00:10:34,700
What?

261
00:10:35,279 --> 00:10:36,480
Want to compete?

262
00:10:37,820 --> 00:10:38,460
Compete in what?

263
00:10:39,360 --> 00:10:40,940
Long-distance running or swimming?

264
00:10:41,759 --> 00:10:43,820
Aren't you afraid your heart disease will act up?

265
00:10:46,940 --> 00:10:48,340
You have heart disease?

266
00:10:49,759 --> 00:10:50,879
This disease...

267
00:10:50,879 --> 00:10:51,980
It's hereditary, right?

268
00:10:52,720 --> 00:10:53,659
I...

269
00:10:53,740 --> 00:10:54,519
I don't...

270
00:10:55,120 --> 00:10:56,460
I didn't tell anyone

271
00:10:57,399 --> 00:10:58,440
I don't have heart disease

272
00:10:58,440 --> 00:10:59,980
Wait, how do you know?

273
00:11:01,460 --> 00:11:03,019
Rheumatic myocarditis

274
00:11:03,740 --> 00:11:05,500
And you're about to have an attack

275
00:11:06,720 --> 00:11:07,679
You're talking nonsense

276
00:11:09,299 --> 00:11:10,580
I advise you

277
00:11:11,080 --> 00:11:13,299
to hurry and get your Bureau Chief dad

278
00:11:13,820 --> 00:11:15,120
to pull some strings for you

279
00:11:15,220 --> 00:11:16,720
and find a better hospital

280
00:11:17,080 --> 00:11:17,940
Because...

281
00:11:18,279 --> 00:11:19,700
within six months

282
00:11:19,759 --> 00:11:22,000
he's going to jail for corruption

283
00:11:22,220 --> 00:11:23,179
You're slandering me

284
00:11:25,019 --> 00:11:26,779
So you're that kind of person

285
00:11:27,000 --> 00:11:28,080
Stay away from me

286
00:11:31,559 --> 00:11:32,580
Just now

287
00:11:32,700 --> 00:11:33,980
you said you liked me

288
00:11:34,539 --> 00:11:35,440
Is that true?

289
00:11:36,100 --> 00:11:36,779
Of course

290
00:11:37,600 --> 00:11:38,080
Come

291
00:11:38,440 --> 00:11:39,139
My dear

292
00:11:39,840 --> 00:11:40,940
Let's go

293
00:11:44,919 --> 00:11:46,259
This hurdle in life

294
00:11:46,820 --> 00:11:47,940
has finally been crossed

295
00:11:49,259 --> 00:11:50,059
Young man

296
00:11:51,259 --> 00:11:52,500
A beautiful future

297
00:11:52,860 --> 00:11:53,720
belongs to you

298
